<typeStatus id="2C29E18FFFF2FFB1EC8CA61AFDCFF8F0" box="[441,545,1841,1866]" pageId="12" pageNumber="485">Holotype</typeStatus>
male from Baker collection labeled &quot;Surigao/ Mindanao/ Baker; USNMENT / 01513419&quot; (
